    Tarantulas was in full speed as he sped across the wide expanse of a 
mountian side, with Terrorsaur above him. He would be at the Bunker soon to 
report to Black Aracnia what had happened, at least she didnt beat her 
minions when they failed, Like Hell Beast and Megatron.
    
    Rampage now had restored all power to the ship and awaited inferno's 
report from Aracnia. At this point he was happy to have her take command of 
things. but, Megatron was lurking about.....
